      <scopecontent id="aspace_f2c61c4af4b42914d6b500f24571e58a">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The materials consist of photographs of Nathaniel Spear, Jr. (Yale 1919) documenting student life at Yale University. Includes views of a dorm room, students on the fence, military training excercises, and a photograph of William H. Taft.</p>  
